<%- include('partials/header') %>
<header>
<% if(user){ %>
    <h1>Hello, <%= user.name %></h1>
    <h4>Welcome Back To Houseplant Legacy!</h4>
<% } else {%> 
    <h1>Hello, Friend</h1>
    <h4>Welcome To Houseplant Legacy!</h4>
<% } %> 
</header>
<main>
    <% if(user){ %>
    <div class="welcome">
        <h4>
            Good to see you again! You know where everything is, so run along and frolick with your Plant Pals.
        </h4>
        <img src="../images/gifs/charlierun.gif" alt="Charlie Brown Racing Across The Screen With a Piece of Paper Clutch In Hand">
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="welcome">
        <img src="../images/gifs/snoopywave.gif" alt="Snoopy Waving With Woody Atop his Red DogHouse">
        <h4>
            We can't wait for you to get settled in and start collecting your dream houseplants! This site is a great way to cultivate your plant-hoarding hobby in advance of or in lieu of the financial and emotional investments houseplants require! Learn a little basic info as you collect them along the way, and break into the practice of plant-sharing within your virtual community!  
        </h4>
        <h4>
            So hop up to the nav bar and log yourself in, we use Google, so no extra password and username to remember! Head on over to the plant shop for a reccomendation to start your collection off with, then check out other Plant Pal's collections for plant clippings they might share with you!    
        </h4>
        <h4>
            If you have any questions, or stories you want to share, head over to our message board where you can post, and reply to other Plant Pal queries!
        </h4>
        <h5>Have Fun!</h5>
    </div>
 <% } %>
    
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
